                        <h1>The Playing Field</h1>
                        <ol class="list-group text-left mt-5">
                            <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-primary">1. The opponent's hand. You cannot see the cards that the opponent has in their hand but you can see how many cards they have left. At the beginning of a player's turn, they will be dealt cards until they have five cards in their hand.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">2. The opponent's goal deck. You can only see the top card of your own and your opponent's goal deck. Each player starts with 15 goal cards at the beginning of the deck. Hover over your own or your opponent's goal deck to see how many cards are left. More about the goal deck can be found in "The Goal" section.</li>
