                <h1 class="mt-5">Getting Started</h1>
                <section class="text-left mx-5">
                    <h4>Make an Account</h4>
                    <p>Making an account is quick and easy, but also required to play. Click the sign up button to sign up with just a username and a password.</p>
                </section>
                <section class="text-left mx-5">
                    <h4>Find a Friend</h4>
                    <p>Card Game is a two player game which means you'll need a friend to play with you. When you and your friend have both made accounts, you can add them by clicking on the "Add Friend" button at the top and searching up their name. They can accept your friend request by pressing the "Pending Friend Requests" button at the top and clicking on the green checkmark.</p>
                </section>
                <section class="text-left mx-5">
                    <h4>Make Sure Your Friend is Online</h4>
                    <p>Your friend will need to be online in order to play with you. To check your online friends, click on the "Friends" button. It tells you how many friends you have online, and shows a dropdown list of all your friends with the online ones highlighted in green.</p>
                </section>
                <section class="text-left mx-5">
                    <h4>Invite Your Friend</h4>
                    <p>If your friend is online, click on the "Friends" button and hover over their name in the dropdown menu. You can invite them by clicking on the green invite button that appears under their name. They will get a notification in the bottom right corner indicating that you have invited them. If they click accept, you will be redirected to the game. You can also check their match history by clicking on "Match History", and you can check your own match history by clicking on the "Signed In As: {username}" button. </p>
                </section>
